    "Ruckman, Dr. Peter S_": "Paul `[char_Paul_Act_13]` winning souls: it is God IN him that is doing the good work, and the Holy Spirit IN him that is producing the right kind of fruit. Paul `[char_Paul_Act_13]` says that in his flesh \u201cdwelleth no good thing\u201d (Rom. 7:18). Get the message? They didn\u2019t at BJU, PCS, BBC, Wheaton, Moody, Fuller, Trinity Evangelical Divinity School, Asbury, Pillsbury, Piedmont, Kings College, Bethel College, or Baylor University.\n1. Peace on earth without \u201cglory to God in the highest\u201d (Luke 2:14).\n1. An old song (see Noah `[char_Noah_Neh_6]`, Gen. 9:21).\n1. Early in the morning (Ps. 5:3).\n1. God had promised Him [v_Gen_1_1] everlasting life before Genesis 1:1.",
